'''Combustion''', also known in [[High Galactic (language)|High Galactic]] as '''''Flamusfracta''''', was an advanced, [[Telekinesis/Legends|telekinetic]] [[The Force/Legends|Force]] [[Force power/Legends|ability]] that allowed users to cause objects to explode by sheer force of will.<ref name="Jedi Path" />

It was rarely used on a person, and the effects it had on inanimate objects and people were devastating. Depending on the size, density and vulnerability of the object in question, combustion would become harder or easier to use successfully. The intensity of the blast could injure an entire room of enemies, particularly if the affected object was made of flammable material.<ref name="Jedi Path" /> [[Yarael Poof/Legends|Yarael Poof]] was known to use this power.<ref name="JVS">[[Jedi vs. Sith: The Essential Guide to the Force (real-life book)|''Jedi vs. Sith: The Essential Guide to the Force'']]</ref>

[[Palpatine/Legends|Darth Sidious]] considered this ability a "mere child's play" in ''[[The Jedi Path: A Manual for Students of the Force]]''.<ref name="Jedi Path" /> After his resurrection on [[Byss/Legends|Byss]], Palpatine used this power to cause a [[Vima-Da-Boda's lightsaber|10,000 year old lightsaber]] to explode in [[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia's]] hands.

